column5: The river was high,fast and dirty.Even the banks were caving in.Yep,the Notty.Same spot Bill M posted about a week or so ago.Im all stuffed up,sorry for the not so clear narratoring.Sounds like I have a cloths peg on my nose.LOLGCD,I found old yeller. Why are my posts coming out this way?
That's not my Ol' Yeller Brian!  ... but that's pretty cool!!!
Hard on the paint when you slam your seat belt in it...  Hit enter after each pic and text line me misguided friend..
He did, I thought that was the problem too but I hit the quote button and everything looks fine.
